Exception handler (INT 0)
Timer Interrupt (INT 1)
Disk Interrupt (INT 2)
Console Interrupt (INT 3)
INT 4 (Create, Delete)
INT 5 (Seek, Open, Close)
6-read
7-write
8-fork
9-Exec
10-exit
INT 11 (Getpid, Getppid, Wait, Signal)
INT 12 (Logout)
INT 13 (Semget, Semrelease)
INT 14 (SemLock, SemUnLock)
15-Shutdown